<br>
First off, Daramor, I posted my simple one line goodbye in alot of forums because I HAVE FRIENDS WHO DONT LOOK ON EVERY BOARD and i wanted them to know im gone so they dont worry, so they dont look for me when im not coming back.<br>
<br>
Secondly and probably the most important, its being circulated, and im sure is already widely known due to the fact that Sarhea has many sympathetic ears to speak into, that i &quot;sabotaged&quot; or attempted to destroy the harvesters of darkness' reputation. I did no such thing.<br>
At first it was a pure evil guild, i liked that, its rare, you dont see many. In my whole time on Fvie which is almost a year i can name maybe three pure evil guilds that take the time to RP. When inthul found out that a gnome warrior of zek and a human wizard who is not a follower of inny or bertox or cazic were let/going to be let in ( and yes he knew in character about demaste, he has his sources ) he was in a bad mood for many reasons and instead of actively spreading that knowledge around he kept his mouth shut for the most part.<br>
What did happen was people who were looking to join would come up and talk to him, ask him questions in character, one of which would often be &quot;is it an evil only guild&quot; ( the question would most often be phrased differently but im too angry to actually RP spell it out at present so i wont )<br>
When asked this question in character he would respond in character, telling that person exactly what he thought. Inthul was never big on lying.<br>
<br>
Finally, you sarhea, this is the soapbox and im pointing the finger for the first and last time at you. Ive spent the last month or more as your friend, yet you turned on me so quickly and im sure youve already convinced yourself that its because i was trying to &quot;hurt your guild&quot;. <br>
Bullshit<br>
Your angry at me because when sarhea practically destroyed inthul's mind i started not talking to you. You wanted to be empathic and &quot;keep me as an ooc friend&quot; but you know what? i personally think what you did when i was gone for one week, only a week mind you, was bad form both in character and out.<br>
That cold shoulder you dont think you deserved was my polite way of dealing with you because i was your friend and i didnt think you wanted me to start ranting at you, which is something i considered but pushed away.<br>
<br>
<br>
To all my friends, goodbye. To everyone on Fvie who has ever roleplayed with one of my characters, goodbye. Im going to miss you all something awful but as it stands ive already deleted my everquest account, thrown out the software and today im buying asherons call 2.<br>
<br>
You know, I spent so much time listening to you bitch as the caring friend sarhea, i never realised how childish you yourself were until i saw it from the other end.<br>
<br>
<br>
Yes i named names, thats what a good flame should do<br>
<br>
This is my final post on the Fvie boards, there will be no others. <br>
