<br>
I would concur.  Others mileage may vary - I think a lot of people are uptight because they fear a 'slippery slope' effect - their 'all evil' Guild lets in some 'evil' humans, and next thing you know there are 'Unkempt Druids' or whatnot... Which might be something they can't stand.<br>
<br>
The same thing is over on the 'Good' side for people who want to play 'reformed' or redeemed Tier'dal or what have you.<br>
<br>
While there is nothing theoretically wrong with those ideas, many people resent the added complication.<br>
<br>
As for Dwarves, I simply forgot to mention them...  You could come up with arguments to have them go either way - part of me likes the idea of having them be 'Good' like the Elves, because they are 'elder' races, but on the other hand, Brell Serillis seems to be a squarely Neutral deity - he did create some of the 'monster' races as well...  but you can counter-argue that his neutrality is reflected in the fact he created both good (Dwarves) and evil (gnolls, kobolds, whatever) in Norrath.<br>
<br>
But ultimately its largely going to be opinion, and those opinions are going to shaped individually.  Elves, Dwarves, and Dragons were not created by Verant.  Virtually everyone going into this game has preconceived notions about what they are.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm49.showMessageRange?topicID=31.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm49.showMessageRange?topicID=31.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm49.showMessageRange?topicID=31.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm49.showMessageRange?topicID=31.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm49.showMessageRange?topicID=31.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm49.showMessageRange?topicID=31.topic&start=121&stop=140>7</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm49.showPrevMessage?topicID=31.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm49.showNextMessage?topicID=31.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm49.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm49.threadControl?topicID=31.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm49.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=31.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to rec